    "Participants Groups Male Female Age Subtotal Total Experimental 30 25 18 Years 55 112 Control 28 29 18 Years 57The quasi-experimental design compares the experimental group, who received instruction enhanced by ChatGPT, with the control group, who were exposed to traditional teaching methods.",
    "Pre-test scores established an equitable starting point for both groups.",
    "Post-test scores then measured the impact of ChatGPT-enhanced instruction.The quantitative analysis assesses the differences in pre-test and post-test scores between the experimental and control groups.",
    "Effect size is computed using Eta square (η 2) to quantify the magnitude of impact.",
    "Sub-skills, including Knowing, Applying, and Reasoning, are examined to ascertain specific areas of improvement.The qualitative analysis augments quantitative findings by exploring participants' experiences."
  ],
